---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — Checklist" description="How Checklist collects and uses your information.">
  <section style="padding-top:56px;">
    <div class="container"><div class="prose">
      <h1 style="font-size:34px;font-weight:800;">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="muted">Last updated: 2026</p>
      <p>When you download a template, we collect your name, email and stated purpose. We use this to deliver the file, improve our templates, and occasionally share useful updates. We never sell your data.</p>
      <h2>What we collect</h2>
      <ul><li>Name and email address you submit</li><li>Which template you downloaded</li></ul>
      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <p>You can request deletion of your data at any time by contacting us.</p>
      <p><em>Note: Replace this placeholder text with your finalized policy before launch.</em></p>
    </div></div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
